{
  "stem": "4513.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had covered mine up, just very carefully, because I said, look.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, anybody that looks different attracts someone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I covered mine up with-- with the garnish that I had on and my nets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and I said, look-- and I took all my stripes off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it wasn't any sense to identify-- everybody knew who I was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, what happened was after Normandy, we went north-- went south to Saint-Lo.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from Saint-Lo, we went southeast to Paris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we're walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think I walked all the way across Europe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyway, we went to-- [LAUGHS] and we got to-- out of the hedgerows, once we were able to fight our way out of the hedgerows.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we were-- and we went to Paris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then from Paris, we went down to Bois-le-Duc, to the Meuse river, in that area, and from-- which was a area under General Patton.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we-- and it-- that was about the time the winter was starting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was-- it was-- it was just cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we-- we went up to [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Malmedy, ?] and the Germans broke through in the Bulge.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- they had told-- they instructed all of us to stop every carriage, every cart, everything that was coming through, and be sure that you-- that there were no Germans in them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because the Germans were coming looking like farmers, and all this sort of thing, and infiltrating behind our lines.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the only thing I remember-- I-- I was in a jeep, with a 30-- I had a Thompson submachine gun.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I re-- and I was-- we were just running to see what we could find.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were checking our area.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I saw these two horses drawing this big cart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I stopped them.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
